room_title: Escape room "Sorcerers' Quest" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Wilmington in Wilmington (DE)
room_description: Enter the world of magic and wizardry by visiting the sorcerer's castle! In this adventure, you must locate your wands and find three powerful treasures in order to vanquish the Dark Lord. Dressed with columns and arches, this experience will take you into the world of illusions! Try to figure your way out of this amazing and magical experience!
